      "text": "On the reasoning front, `Max`  is the newest and highest reasoning **effort**. Use it for your most demanding for demanding tasks that need more exploration and verification.\n\nSeparately, `Pro` mode  is a reasoning **mode**, that performs more model work to improve",
      "url": "https://x.com/gabrielchua/status/2076305043935166547",
      "post_type": "original",
