      "organization": "OpenAI",
      "source_type": "employee",
      "priority": "P0",
      "published_at": "2026-07-12T21:57:53+08:00",
      "text": "Persisted Reasoning  allows you to reuse available reasoning items across turns to improve multi-turn quality and cache efficiency.\n\nAnd on the cache, explicit caching  lets you mark exactly which reusable prompt prefixes OpenAI caches.",
