      "text": "New API updates with the GPT-5.6 family of models! \n\nFirst up,  `multi-agent` is available in beta, allowing a model to spin up and coordinate subagents in parallel, synthesizing their work to provide a final response.\n\n\nhttps://\ndevelopers.openai.com/api/docs/guide\ns/responses-multi-agent\n…",
      "url": "https://x.com/gabrielchua/status/2076305034447626482",
      "post_type": "original",
      "is_pinned": false,
